{
  "stem": "4963.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I learned Lithuanian, because everything was Lithuanian.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was the only Jewish girl in our [INAUDIBLE] gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I worked day and night, studied day and night, and my aunt and uncle were, again, very nice to me, provided me with all.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You know, we-- we had a little apartment.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We all lived-- let's see, one, two, three, four, I think there were six of us in one room.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And one room was a kitchen, one was a living room, and one was an-- an office for my uncle and one was an office for my aunt.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We knew-- of course we didn't-- in those days we had no correspondence, so I didn't know anything about my parents.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Someone mentioned that they were-- they were sent out to Siberia, but we had no correspondence at all.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and we didn't really-- and the war was still on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The concentration camps were still on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was 1944.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we knew that my Aunt Paula, Chassia, Osher, they were all sent out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Where, we didn't know anything about them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we stuck together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My aunt-- Leiba and Hanna and the children and-- my-- my cousins.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I went to school, and it was of utmost importance to me to study and to, you know, do well.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I would grab hold of everybody I-- I could find to help me with math, with history, with-- to catch up and everything that I needed.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Lithuanians were running the school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Russian was a language that was required, but Lithuanian-- it was a Lithuanian school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, all over.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was secret police, and you had to be very careful what you said, how you said.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you couldn't earn very much money or else they would be confiscated.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
